[Ugh.]

GOKU: Mmm...

OOLONG [deadpan]: What a miracle we have witnessed.
Allow me to go call the local news.
CHI-CHI: I've had to deal with him screaming bloody murder for the last three hours; I'll take what I can get.

TENSHINHAN: Shut up!

TENSHINHAN: Aaand here we go...

You'll never be as strong as a Super Saiyan.

[Give it 7 years. It'll be even *less* of a milestone.]

You know he can kill you, right?

If he gives in, I win...

TRICLOPS: At this point, it's a game.
If he gives in, I win... and he knows that.

timeline, then's there gotta be one in this timeline too.

sorry my Dad killed Chiaotzu.

Hey, so, if I were a gambling man...
